    <p class="lead" style="font-size: 150%;">Life is too short for reading twenty-year-old books.<br>Learn BASIC and Assembly with bite-sized video tutorials.</p> 
    <h2>Someday you WILL write a game or a demo!</h2>
    <p>Too bad your daily job sucks most of your time, so there is not much left for your hobby.</p>

    <p>You have NO TIME for listening long boring lectures, trying understand outdated tutorials and begging for help on forums.</p>

    <p>But someday you will have time for that...</p>

    <p>Someday you will write a game or a demo...</p>

    <h2>What if you could learn something new in 5 minutes?</h2>

    <p>Imagine that 5 minutes from now <strong>you will know</strong> how to define Sprite Bitmaps in Assembly.</p>

    <p>Ready?</p>

    <p>Watch this video:</p>
    <% sprite_episode = episodes_catalog.find_episode(22) %>
    
